Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著色真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆觸也相當地精巧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然之前也有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒想到國外的畫竟能達到如此境界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監察使來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幅禁品我收走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼同好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幕府的走狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 再請一個幫手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和黑衣鯖人的一戰使我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸刀流的劍士並非等閒之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万次哥很強 還是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是個可以依靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過再多一個人的話就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個幫手 有人選了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找了很久了 現在終於給我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞藝術我管不著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是之後收拾房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給房東道歉的可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗理老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小凜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小辰還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是女大十八變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可不是來拜年的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不就是個普通的畫師麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡像一個劍術高強的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去也像是從小被雙親遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後被好心的猴子收養
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近才來到人類世界的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的保鏢 或者說是幫手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 就是這種感覺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅野他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小和他一起長大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 本想早點告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 該說抱歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連葬禮都沒能參加 深感抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要復仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先想想你自己的實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓你去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這只是個愚蠢的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天津這個人 我也有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為天才的22歲劍客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保鏢也好 幫手也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫健次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是万次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雇他一個人能幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許確實做不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是除了万次哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能有一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長崎屋先生來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妨不妨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思 讓您親自跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一種顏色確定下來之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一幅讓我滿意的作品了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這幅畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我畫一幅新的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要這麼做嗎 凜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就好了 不要動好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把老師的力量借給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見 我只是個畫師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜託的不是作為畫師的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作為朝廷監察使的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是父親告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅野這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個讓人頭疼的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說老師之所以會被僱用為監察使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為老師的人脈和劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且您的劍術在父親之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把劍拿起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫師如果不接觸新鮮事物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫技和內心都會生銹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說新鮮事物…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是外國的藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如今這個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果私藏這些物品馬上就會被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我想到了一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓自己成為監察使不就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了取得幕府的垂青 我不斷地磨練劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊走全國搜集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後以各種名義…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說是反幕府的軍士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同為畫師的同伴我也殺過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求藝術的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要超越常理 尋求新的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有再大的犧牲我也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既是說我的劍已十分骯髒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法幫你什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 你就誠實點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那裝好人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說穿了你不就是在為自己著想麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的真好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是用一些亂七八糟的歪理給自己找理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:12:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼藝術不藝術的 其實什麼都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是個畜生罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可笑至極
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万次哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是不想拿自己的命去冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不否認這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有很多想畫的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得這是什麼丟人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術家都會這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個白髮佬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万次哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚和小辰一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 他不會不管你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是個脾氣暴躁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你的生日我居然遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小凜你哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一個可怕的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個貪睡的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就一直沉睡下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手不錯嘛 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住四處亂飛的蝴蝶 是相當快樂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万次哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在想鯖人怎麼會輸給這麼一個小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽好了 砍下他的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要報了這個仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯖人的部下就是我們的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這不符合逸刀流的門規
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它呢 殺了再說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉囉嗦嗦的說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打就快打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想打就滾回去睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝好漢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你那一把刀能對付得了我們這麼多人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正有此意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 從我家那邊傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個顏色也不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經信誓旦旦選擇的繪畫道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只有這種水準
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀 哪裡有刀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 你這個臭婆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往哪跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來陪你們玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經數次遇見過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用什麼來形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花？夕陽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一種接近根源的深邃而高貴的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來很容易 可是這到底是哪種紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 請給我惡魔的指示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找的就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是根源的紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這個顏色的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:17:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了吧 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為底下是松樹皮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以興奮過頭的傻瓜會以為只是些普通的毛刺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万次哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 凜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到一個好主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你面前把這個女人撕碎如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 你試試看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到本人會同意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 禿子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣露骨地說別人的缺陷可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万次哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招式很一般嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褻瀆藝術品的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸刀流唯一的門規是一對一對決
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違反門規者…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕對沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙阿葉山大人提拔 得以進入本家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小人真琴 現在此地任職
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那麼下面的事交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無法理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與浅野家毫無關係的你為什麼要參與進來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不惜弄得遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你嘲笑過我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你是陶醉在為他人犧牲的感覺中麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是為何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我 其實都是同類
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人也是一項藝術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我和你扯在一起 白髮佬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毋須擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會按期完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為畫具費 我要收取30兩黃金
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能幫你什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我把屍體都買下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實都是同類嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重啊 小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜就交給你了 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這混蛋 結果還是沒記住我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 万次哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.17,0:24:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚犯
